# API Contract Review Routing

Use the most specific contract skill.

## Routing

- Games Labs API, mobile, gateway, missions, wallet, VIP, store, or provider-facing flow -> `ai-skills/skills/games-labs-api-review/SKILL.md`
- gRPC, protobuf, grpc-gateway, generated artifacts, field numbers, or enum compatibility -> `ai-skills/skills/grpc-contract-review/SKILL.md`
- Generic API/proto/mobile/web contract changes -> `ai-skills/skills/api-contract-review/SKILL.md`

## Rules

1. Do not approve contract changes from summaries alone.
2. Check backward compatibility, client rollout, error/status behavior, and generated artifacts.
3. Source code, `.proto` files, generated outputs, tests, CI, and logs override skill guidance.
